      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo contains a snapshot of the state of standardization of protocols used in the Internet as of July 22, 2004.  It lists official protocol standards and Best Current Practice RFCs; it is not a complete index to the RFC series.  The latest version of this memo is designated STD 1. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
